Paul Boesch https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Boesch 0 Paul Max Boesch (October 2, 1912 – March 7, 1989) was a professional wrestler and promoter, most famous for his work as an announcer and promoter for Houston Wrestling. He also spent several stints working with the Universal Wrestling Federation, World Class Championship Wrestling, Jim Crockett Promotions, and the World Wrestling Federation.
